INSERT INTO `fs_news` VALUES (789, '<p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n&nbsp; <o:AllowPNG/>\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <w:WordDocument>\n&nbsp; <w:View>Normal</w:View>\n&nbsp; <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\n&nbsp; <w:TrackMoves/>\n&nbsp; <', '&nbsp;\n\n<h2 class=\"text-align-center\">Vietnam’s Brainiest Kid contestants reunite at TH School</h2>\n\n\n\n\n<p>This morning, nearly 50 of the top contestants from the television show Chinh Phục, Vietnam’s Brainiest Kid, had a chance to reunite before the finale airs. They were joined by parents and siblings as they were warmly welcomed to the school by members of Senior Leadership, teachers and current students. As parents attended seminars on the educational programs offered to our secondary students, the contestants were treated to lessons in English, chemistry, and art.</p><p>The top three contestants in Chinh Phục have been offered scholarships to attend TH School in the coming academic year. Hai An, one of the top Chinh Phục contestants, reflected on his experience at the reunion, “What impresses me most about TH School is the friendly and enthusiastic teachers. The classes also have many interesting activities, making it easier to understand in lessons.”</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"\n  sqs-gallery-container\n  sqs-gallery-block-slideshow\n  \n  \n  sqs-gallery-has-controls\n  sqs-gallery-has-thumbnails\n\n  \n    sqs-gallery-block-show-meta sqs-gallery-block-meta-position-bottom\n    \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  clear\"\n  \n  \n>\n  <div class=\"sqs-gallery\">\n    \n      \n\n        \n          \n            <div class=\"slide content-fill\" data-type=\"image\" data-click-through-url=\"\">\n              \n                <noscript><img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/59f286aa4c0dbf9244a43d28/1517388980976-7KBER5BPI1CUTIX4OA4N/27355823_919580654867036_5023476387901567683_o.jpg\" alt=\"27355823_919580654867