e and screen including popular songs from the musical, \'The Lion King\' along with songs from the films \'Aquaman\', \'The Greatest Showman\', \'Twilight\', and many more!</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">The audience was very excited and our students were well prepared to put on amazing performances. Thank you to the students for your hard work, the parents for their support, and our music teachers for constantly bringing the school’s music program to the next level!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<div class=\"\n  sqs-gallery-container\n  sqs-gallery-block-slideshow\n  \n  \n  \n  sqs-gallery-has-thumbnails\n\n  \n    sqs-gallery-block-show-meta sqs-gallery-block-meta-position-bottom\n    \n  \n  sqs-gallery-block-show-meta\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\n  \n  block-animation-none\n  clear\"\n  \n  \n>\n  <div class=\"sqs-gallery\">\n    \n      \n\n        \n          \n            <div class=\"slide content-fill\" data-type=\"image\" data-click-through-url=\"\">\n              \n                <noscript><img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/59f286aa4c0dbf9244a43d28/1617265788309-P2JTJZV1BLQDUKL5KKR6/128807508_1748237598668000_8029218201163706867_n.jpg\" alt=\"128807508_1748237598668000_8029218201163706867_n.jpg\" /></noscript><img class=\"thumb-image\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/59f286aa4c0dbf9244a43d28/1617265788309-P2JTJZV1BLQDUKL5KKR6/128807508_1748237598668000_8029218201163706867_n.jpg\" data-image=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/59f286aa4c0dbf9244a43d28/1617265788309-P2JTJZV1BLQDUKL5KKR6/128807508_1748237598668000_8029218201163706867_n.jpg\" data-image-dimensions=\"2048x1365\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" alt=\"128807508_1748237598668000_8029218201163706867_n.jpg\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"60658478975e2914766602a4\" data-type=\"image\" />\n              \n\n              \n                \n              \n              <div class=\"color-overlay\"></div>\n            </di