INSERT INTO `fs_news_en` VALUES (912, 'On April 23rd, at TH School – Hoa Lac boarding campus, more than 60 students and parents have joined TH School Open House to discover the “2 in 1” boarding model in their amazement.', '<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">On April 23rd, at TH School – Hoa Lac boarding campus, more than 60 students and parents have joined TH School Open House to discover the “2 in 1” boarding model in their amazement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">The tour to the 25,000m2 campus has left the visitors with a lot of surprises, about the modern facilities, classrooms, diverse functional rooms that meet the needs of all students. Most importantly, the boarding house is the highlight of the trip, as students and parents have witnessed the high-quality living space of TH School students, where they can be independent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">At the event, parents also met and talked with Mr Stephen West, Superintendent of TH Schools, to find out more about the innovative learning programs and the boarding model at Hoa Lac campus. The students had so much fun taking part in STEM activities, sports competitions with our TH School boarding students and enjoyed the scrumptious yet delicious lunch at the canteen after all the fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Hien Khanh – a 9th grader who joined the event could not help her excitement when sharing with us: “It is safe here, with a fresh and green environment. Teachers and students are friendly and open, which makes me feel more than comfortable. If I start my journey here, I hope I will become more independent and gain new experiences.”</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"sqs-gallery-container\r\n  sqs-gallery-block-grid\r\n  sqs-gallery-aspect-ratio-square\r\n  sqs-gallery-thumbnails-per-row-4\r\n  \r\n  \r\n